column3: It's not yet fetched by Transifex, hope this happens over the next hours and then the translators can start their work :).\n
@laanwj It's still not available on Transifex. @tcatm Can you check what's wrong here or tell me how I / we can force Transifex to fetch the new master file?\n
Is transifex supposed to fetch it, or do you need to push it with a script?\n
It showed up a few minutes ago ... don't know if tcatm did something or if the fetch interval is that long.\n
I think they only fetch about once per day.\n
